data.description: This home is the REASON you want to move. This 4 bed/ 2.5 bath traditional brick home has lots to offer with spacious rooms, split bedroom floor plan and a breakfast bar for everyone. You'll love the open concept design that features elegant archways built with style. Perfect fenced yard for the fido in your life. New roof installed Aug 2021. Buyers, all you have to do is move in. CALL immediately for a buyers tour. Seller will pay up to 4k in closing costs or buy down.
